04:34.550 --> 04:36.483
They call this
the Buffalo valley.

04:38.381 --> 04:40.418
- Are there buffalo in it?

04:40.487 --> 04:44.422
- Yeah, well, sometimes they'll
wander up from the park...

04:44.491 --> 04:48.080
In 1889, when they thought
all the buffalo were gone,

04:48.149 --> 04:52.706
