told 'em "no",

04:55.329 --> 04:58.539
'cause he thought they wanted
to kill the rest,

04:58.608 --> 05:02.129
but he knew where they were.

05:02.198 --> 05:03.337
They were right here.

05:06.098 --> 05:08.480
When the park started
to protect the buffalo,

05:08.549 --> 05:10.551
