05:39.304 --> 05:41.686
Well, the Army
just wanted them gone.

05:44.620 --> 05:45.828
- Why'd the army want 'em gone?

05:47.174 --> 05:50.246
- Because they wanted
the Indians gone,

05:50.315 --> 05:52.213
and buffalo is what
Indians depended on.

05:54.768 --> 05:59.359
Now the buffalo live
on ranches or preserves.

06:01.188 --> 06:03.017
Not much different
for the Indians.

06:07.194 --> 06:08.678
- That's not fair.

06:08.747 --> 06:09.783
- No.

06:10.922 --> 06:12.855
- Let me...

06:15.582 --> 06:19.379
fair means one side got
exactly what they wanted

06:19.448 --> 06:21.588
