07:19.335 --> 07:21.095
- What the fuck
are you doing?

07:23.788 --> 07:25.445
You don't know
how lucky you are.

07:26.756 --> 07:29.414
Your coma, that was
a gift from God.

07:31.140 --> 07:35.351
I had to watch it.

07:37.180 --> 07:40.183
I watched pus and bile bubble
out of you.

07:40.252 --> 07:43.186
Here. And here.
Here.

07:43.255 --> 07:47.674
And here for 60 fucking days,

07:47.743 --> 07:51.471
I had to watch the life
leak out of you.

07:51.540 --> 07:53.956
And then you look for
a way to lose it again.

07:54.025 --> 07:56.752
You fucking seek it...

07:56.821 --> 07:58.995
Well, I'm not doing that again.

07:59.064 --> 08:02.136
I am not willing you back
to life the next time you die.

08:02.205 --> 08:03.724
- What was I supposed
to do, Beth?

08:05.692 --> 08:07.694
Let a dozen people
get killed for the change

08:07.763 --> 08:09.558
in their pocket--
- Yes!

08:09.627 --> 08:12.181
Because when you die
everything that you fought for--

08:12.250 --> 08:14.942
and everything that you had me
fight for dies with you.

08:15.011 --> 08:16.047
- I'm not made like that, honey.

08:16.116 --> 08:17.669
- Then get fucking remade!

08:28.404 --> 08:31.027
I fight so hard for you, Dad.

08:31.096 --> 08:32.995
And you do nothing to help me.

08:35.791 --> 08:37.517
You do the opposite.

08:37.586 --> 08:40.036
- I do what's right
in my heart.

08:40.105 --> 08:43.971
What's in my soul
and I won't stop.

08:44.040 --> 08:46.180
I won't stop for anyone
including you.

08:46.249 --> 08:48.010
- You look for justice
everywhere.

08:48.079 --> 08:50.944
Everywhere but the mirror.

08:51.013 --> 08:54.464
Where's the justice for the man
who tried to kill you? Huh?

08:54.534 --> 08:57.606
You will risk your life
for strangers,

08:57.675 --> 09:01.644
but what are you risking to find
the man who fucking did this?

09:01.713 --> 09:03.094
Dad, look at it!

09:13.242 --> 09:15.900
You won't look

09:15.969 --> 09:17.108
because you know who did it.

09:19.662 --> 09:23.390
You have some...

09:23.459 --> 09:26.358
false connection with him.
You think he's your child?

09:26.427 --> 09:29.154
Fine.
No, think it. I don't care.

09:29.223 --> 09:34.366
But your child, he burned
the skin from me.

09:34.435 --> 09:35.747
And you've done nothing
about it...

09:38.578 --> 09:39.648
- It wasn't Jamie.

09:39.717 --> 09:41.960
- Stop lying to yourself.

09:42.029 --> 09:43.272
- It wasn't Jamie.

09:46.586 --> 09:48.518
His name is Terrell Riggins.

09:53.006 --> 09:54.697
He's serving life in prison.

09:57.493 --> 09:59.702
He attacked us to send a
message to rival gang members

09:59.771 --> 10:01.531
that he wasn't weak.

10:01.601 --> 10:04.086
That we didn't destroy him.

10:04.155 --> 10:05.639
He is an animal
trying to convince

10:05.708 --> 10:07.365
other animals he's still strong.

10:08.435 --> 10:09.678
We proved he wasn't.

10:12.439 --> 10:16.270
If he's alive,
and I doubt he is,

10:16.339 --> 10:18.410
he's hiding behind his bunk
with his teeth bared,

10:18.479 --> 10:19.895
waiting to die because
that's what animals do

10:19.964 --> 10:21.137
when they're cornered.

10:22.760 --> 10:24.244
And that animal is cornered.

10:27.523 --> 10:29.870
- So we do nothing about it?

10:29.939 --> 10:33.322
- What are you
asking me, Beth?

10:33.391 --> 10:37.119
You asking me to waste
my life on that piece of shit?

10:42.331 --> 10:43.504
- No, Daddy.

10:45.610 --> 10:47.336
That's what my life's for.

11:05.492 --> 11:07.701
- Beth...

11:14.708 --> 11:16.020
- Hello?

11:16.089 --> 11:18.332
- <i>This is a collect call
from Park County Jail.</i>

11:18.401 --> 11:19.851
<i>Caller, say your name.</i>

11:19.920 --> 11:21.266
<i>- Summer.</i>

11:22.267 --> 11:23.648
- I accept.

11:23.717 --> 11:26.375
<i>- John? The DA's asking
for life in prison.</i>

11:26.444 --> 11:27.756
<i>Life!</i>

11:27.825 --> 11:29.102
- For what?

11:29.171 --> 11:31.276
<i>- Protesting the airport.</i>

11:31.345 --> 11:33.762
- Oh, God. All right.

11:35.625 --> 11:36.972
I'm on my way.
Just stay there.

11:39.146 --> 11:40.734
I'm sorry, that was
a dumb thing to say.

11:41.770 --> 11:42.840
I'm on my way...

11:50.606 --> 11:53.195
<i>- As more information comes out
about the horrific shootout</i>

11:53.264 --> 11:55.749
<i>at the Ruby's Cafe
in Belgrade yesterday,</i>

11:55.818 --> 11:58.200
<i>the assailants have
been identified as members</i>

11:58.269 --> 12:00.581
<i>of a local militia that
has been the subject of</i>

12:00.650 --> 12:03.274
<i>a continued operation between
the Sheriff's department</i>

12:03.343 --> 12:05.310
<i>and Livestock Agents
that has now</i>

12:05.379 --> 12:08.313
<i>taken the life of
Park County's own Sheriff.</i>

12:08.382 --> 12:10.177
<i>The armed robbery interrupted</i>

12:10.246 --> 12:12.283
<i>by Former Livestock
Commissioner John Dutton</i>

12:12.352 --> 12:14.354
<i>would have certainly
led to a greater loss</i>

12:14.423 --> 12:16.874
<i>of innocent life
had he not intervened.</i>

12:16.943 --> 12:20.291
<i>John Dutton's acceptance speech
of Governor Perry's endorsement</i>

12:20.360 --> 12:22.914
<i>seemed odd and out
of touch when he gave it.</i>

12:22.983 --> 12:25.986
<i>Now, it has
the ring of prophecy.</i>

12:26.055 --> 12:29.541
<i>- There is a war being
waged against our way of life.</i>

12:29.610 --> 12:30.922
<i>They will tell you
all the reasons</i>

12:30.991 --> 12:33.753
<i>why our way of life
is bad for Montana.</i>

12:33.822 --> 12:36.203
<i>The ugly truth is
they want the land.</i>

12:36.272 --> 12:40.621
<i>And if they get it, it will
never look like our land again.</i>

12:40.690 --> 12:42.658
<i>That is progress
in today's terms.</i>

12:42.727 --> 12:47.111
<i>So if it's progress you seek,
do not vote for me.</i>

12:47.180 --> 12:49.527
<i>I am the opposite of progress.</i>

12:49.596 --> 12:52.461
<i>I am the wall
that it bashes against.</i>

12:52.530 --> 12:54.981
<i>And I will not
be the one who breaks.</i>

12:55.050 --> 12:57.466
<i>No, Mister Dutton.
It doesn't appear you will.</i>

13:00.296 --> 13:02.920
- Now he gets to be the hero on
top of fucking everything else.

13:02.989 --> 13:04.853
No, no, no...

13:04.922 --> 13:07.303
He just gave you a window.

13:07.372 --> 13:08.857
- What window?

13:08.926 --> 13:10.617
