Missoula, and Helena.

13:38.541 --> 13:41.544
Be the face
of pragmatic progressivism.

13:41.613 --> 13:46.170
Be the bridge and
you will be Governor.

13:46.239 --> 13:47.930
Okay, now is when we
separate from him.

13:47.999 --> 13:49.414
Introduce Montana
to your real father.

13:51.209 --> 13:53.142
- Um...

13:56.525 --> 13:58.320
