13:58.389 --> 13:59.977
We're just gonna walk
and talk some strategy.

14:00.046 --> 14:01.150
- You do that, son.

14:04.740 --> 14:09.124
- Um... I don't think we want
to bring my father into this.

14:09.193 --> 14:10.919
- Now's the perfect time.

14:10.988 --> 14:12.852
- He was in prison.

14:12.921 --> 14:14.060
- What for?

14:16.821 --> 14:18.374
- Murder.

14:24.691 --> 14:27.107
Who?

14:27.176 --> 14:28.384
Who did he murder?

14:30.593 --> 14:31.594
- My mother.

14:32.595 --> 14:33.838
- Your mother?

14:36.461 --> 14:38.670
And you're just
telling me this now.

14:38.739 --> 14:41.052
- It was 40 years ago.

14:41.121 --> 14:44.676
And he paid his debt.
I have forgiven him.

14:44.745 --> 14:48.784
-
How noble, Jamie.
That's just great.

14:48.853 --> 14:50.027
Do you think the
voters of Montana

14:50.096 --> 14:51.304
are going to forgive him too?

14:51.373 --> 14:53.962
- The voters of Montana
don't need to know.

14:54.031 --> 14:57.310
- How can someone so brilliant
be so fucking stupid?

15:00.900 --> 15:02.625
Your birth certificate
becomes public record

15:02.694 --> 15:04.455
when you run for office.

15:04.524 --> 15:06.250
