and get him out of your life.

15:40.042 --> 15:41.526
- She's not wrong, son.

15:44.460 --> 15:46.186
If I'm going to be
a liability for you...

15:46.255 --> 15:48.257
Maybe I better just...

15:48.326 --> 15:50.225
make myself scarce for a while.

15:50.294 --> 15:52.123
- I don't want you to do that.

15:52.192 --> 15:53.745
- I know you don't.

15:53.814 --> 15:56.196
