all the times in your life

15:56.265 --> 16:00.960
where what you wanted was
the worst thing for you.

16:34.510 --> 16:37.030
- Not used to seeing you
come in through the front door.

16:37.099 --> 16:41.276
- Yeah.
Might be the first time.

16:41.345 --> 16:43.278
Drug a few in through
the back, though, didn't we?

16:43.347 --> 16:45.004
- That we did.

16:45.073 --> 16:47.144
- Who's Watch Commander?

16:47.213 --> 16:50.871
- Ramsey, till
the end of the day.

16:50.940 --> 16:52.356
- He retiring?

16:52.425 --> 16:54.358
- Appointed him interim Sheriff.

16:54.427 --> 16:56.084
- Not Sam?

16:57.740 --> 16:58.741
- Not Sam.

17:10.408 --> 17:13.032
- John, how are you.

17:13.101 --> 17:16.794
- Well, I'm breathing, Bill.

17:16.863 --> 17:19.279
