I don't need a statement

17:19.348 --> 17:22.075
from you beyond what we have.

17:22.144 --> 17:24.215
County attorney is
compiling witness statements,

17:24.284 --> 17:26.976
and that's gonna take a while.

17:27.046 --> 17:29.358
- Not why I'm here.

17:29.427 --> 17:30.739
May I sit?

17:30.808 --> 17:32.741
- Please.

17:32.810 --> 17:34.501
- Against my better judgment,

17:34.570 --> 17:37.504
I'm looking into this case
against Summer Higgins.

17:40.404 --> 17:43.269
- Two felony assault
against peace officer charges,

17:43.338 --> 17:46.789
on two separate occasions
which makes it habitual.

17:46.858 --> 17:49.896
There's criminal trespass,
reckless endangerment,

17:49.965 --> 17:51.863
resisting arrest.

17:51.932 --> 17:54.176
- Life in prison, Bill?

17:54.245 --> 17:55.833
- I'm not the prosecutor, John.

17:59.664 --> 18:01.080
- May I see her?

18:02.081 --> 18:04.773
