18:05.912 --> 18:07.845
- She's in with
the public defender now.

18:09.157 --> 18:10.606
Want to sit in with them?

18:11.849 --> 18:12.850
- If I could.

18:18.027 --> 18:21.790
- 149263 in Interview One.

18:21.859 --> 18:24.517
Ask the inmate if she would
like John Dutton to join them.

18:29.556 --> 18:30.661
- So, Sheriff.

18:30.730 --> 18:34.113
- <i>Interim Sheriff.</i>

18:34.182 --> 18:36.839
- We both know where that leads.

18:36.908 --> 18:38.531
Big shoes to fill.

18:38.600 --> 18:39.773
- You think so?

18:40.774 --> 18:42.259
- Don't you?

18:42.328 --> 18:45.745
- Donnie was a gambling
addict and an alcoholic

18:45.814 --> 18:49.645
who only protected
and served the highest bidder.

18:49.714 --> 18:51.302
- He was a father.

18:51.371 --> 18:54.305
- Half the men in my jail
are fathers.

19:00.725 --> 19:02.451
On our way.

19:04.246 --> 19:05.661
- I know where it is.

19:05.730 --> 19:08.975
- Things will be different
with me in charge.

19:09.044 --> 19:11.253
- New rules, huh?

19:11.322 --> 19:12.668
- Still the old rules.

19:12.737 --> 19:15.084
But now they'll be enforced.

19:15.154 --> 19:16.948
- Oh.

19:17.017 --> 19:19.088
So the county can
sleep good tonight.

19:26.958 --> 19:29.409
- I will ask that both Class B
felonies be dropped.

19:31.100 --> 19:33.758
In exchange, we don't contest
class D reckless endangerment.

19:33.827 --> 19:35.035
Pull up a seat.

19:36.968 --> 19:38.763
