trespass will likely be

19:38.832 --> 19:40.213
dropped to a misdemeanor.

19:40.282 --> 19:43.975
- I didn't assault him,
I pushed him back.

19:44.044 --> 19:45.322
- That's assault.

19:45.391 --> 19:48.117
- Well, technically,
it's battery.

19:50.223 --> 19:51.811
- Do you want to try the case?

19:51.880 --> 19:53.571
